syslog(3) for Haskell_
======================

:Latest Release: syslog-1.1.tar.gz_
:Darcs:          darcs_ get --partial http://cryp.to/syslog/

Synopsis
--------

  The ``Syslog.hs`` modules provides FFI bindings to
  ``syslog(3)``. The bindings are somewhat incomplete, i.e. there
  is no way to set log-masks. Patches are welcome. Process the
  file with ``hsc2hs`` to obtain a usable Haskell module.

Documentation
-------------

  `Reference Documentation`_
     Haddock-generated reference of all exported
     functions.

